 Runners will take off at the Nkangala District Municipality in Middelburg and will then proceed to run along the R555(Old Witbank road). The course will take them to OR Tambo Street where the participants will then turn left into Mona Street and then right into Bethal Street. From there on, the joggers will turn left in Mandela road and proceed to Witbank Dam. Also read: GTR2018 has arrived! The mentioned roads will be affected by a partial road closure during the event and motorists are urged to use alternative routes. A map of the running trail has been laid out for the convenience of our readers.  Image generated by www.mobserver.co.za • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za